Hi,
 With 2.6.11-rc1 bk6 and bk7 (didn't tried with < bk6), my alps touchpad is no 
more correctly probed, it's recognised as a standard PS/2 mouse.
 So, with this trivial two line patch, everything is working again.
Cheers.
